{"tid":1497831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"823人鏈分佈建議","createTime":"2019-08-23T06:54:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T10:21:30.000Z","uid":119908,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fbdfd0f8383d7e4e0ad0e7184d1abb6f8678527d","tid":1497831,"uid":119908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T06:54:12.000Z","msg":"(代朋友po)<br />\n<br />\n根據Google Form嘅人數比例結果，我做咗個地圖版本，大家可以參考下邊啲集合點比較多人，邊啲位少人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OW1E7Em.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOW1E7Em.jpg&h=4b3d6353&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家見到個集合點非常綠，可以考慮下去啲紅嘅地區<br />\n[綠同紅要顏色]<br />\n<br />\n例如: <br />\n荃灣線方面<br />\n荃灣比較夠人 (-&gt;大窩口)<br />\n旺角比較夠人 (-&gt;石硤尾等自動補位)<br />\n星光大道個choice我諗未必咁多人見到個選項先低比例<br />\n<br />\n港島方面<br />\n中環比較夠人 (-&gt;上環/西營盤，小心)<br />\n筲箕灣亦比較夠人 (-&gt;鰂魚涌，小心)<br />\n等等等等<br />\n<br />\n[所有括號連埋下面都要細字]<br />\n<br />\n數字只供參考<br />\n最重要都係大家要出席<br />\n19:00集合, 20:00-21-00 組成人鏈<br />\n<br />\n實際情況到時留意即時消息be water <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/HKWay\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKWay&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1U6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=8f5bb14e\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKWay</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(百分比數字同Google form有唔同嘅base<br />\n以下小小解釋<br />\n不論夠唔夠人，如果目標係盡量平均分佈人數<br />\n所以用比例計算，而非人數<br />\n例如荃灣需要全活動2%人<br />\n但係在Google form 有7%揀荃灣<br />\n因此荃灣比例有350% ;<br />\n相對於大窩口~50%的話<br />\n意思即係在一路段, 荃灣會有7個人, 大窩口只有1個人<br />\n太複雜就出左黎先!)<br />\n<br />\n(數字取於8/23 00:00 約3萬回應)<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無懼白色恐怖<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"cf3206c6313716d280a289f291155202e0e840c0","tid":1497831,"uid":242737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T06:55:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd8e7a1e62cbe260d0165c7114d7fcf1b9e964b9","tid":1497831,"uid":67315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T06:55:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70c36e4d195f95b6642659db29d55f44a002cb40","tid":1497831,"uid":40356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T06:57:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7f68737bc1a04dc90401af86c9ee9abe2a462717","tid":1497831,"uid":119908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T06:57:38.000Z","msg":"無幫手改到排板sorry <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家斟酌睇下啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bda399a3b64f430395ba25c2a935bed1994cba4","tid":1497831,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T06:57:43.000Z","msg":"點解隔離個po又好似話全部都缺人咁<br />\n<br />\n今晚「香港之路」手拖手活動以下地區嚴重唔夠人呀！！！！！！！快啲call馬<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1497758\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1497758</a>"},{"pid":"23fc8f137acffb52ea46c206aee370dca843fe68","tid":1497831,"uid":174936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T06:59:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"754b996ad0802c346c97189f9c8ff521fe56c658","tid":1497831,"uid":119908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bda399a3b64f430395ba25c2a935bed1994cba4","tid":1497831,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T06:57:43.000Z","msg":"點解隔離個po又好似話全部都缺人咁<br />\n<br />\n今晚「香港之路」手拖手活動以下地區嚴重唔夠人呀！！！！！！！快啲call馬<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1497758\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1497758</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:01:27.000Z","msg":"有啲站係特別少人<br />\n建議未填form個班可以去揀位填窿"},{"pid":"0febc6ba7e809188294111f7ffac043a08493faa","tid":1497831,"uid":210233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:06:01.000Z","msg":"幸好多人少人站往往相鄰,可以自然走位"},{"pid":"ce508577063ea749ae1b908dd6fd863c60215637","tid":1497831,"uid":11990