e":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:20:04.000Z","msg":"推上去呀"},{"pid":"6e52ef35e8b92e841ac72162515d1e34cda8ced2","tid":1497831,"uid":66221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:20:58.000Z","msg":"其他地方都要人呀"},{"pid":"e3382614c8f3250bad478e188306c2eb3f9c2646","tid":1497831,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:21:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"38994f7bdc168818b7f703ddc176950c0b6bd35e","tid":1497831,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:21:30.000Z","msg":"<strong>聽日824對家吹大雞發動萬人圍港台<br />\n中共又發動宣傳機器想港台跪同清洗</strong><br />\n<br />\n營救香港電台！對家堅吹大雞萬人圍 配合國家機器滅利君雅鏗鏘集頭條新聞聲<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/afeaiKU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/afeaiKU</a><br />\n<br />\n大家要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>一人一信撐港台<br />\n去信廣管局</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ba_archives.ofca.gov.hk/cn/contact/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fba_archives.ofca.gov.hk%2Fcn%2Fcontact%2F&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1U6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=2b197573\" target=\"_blank\">https://ba_archives.ofca.gov.hk/cn/contact/</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">依個唔算投訴，咪當意見咁send<br />\n記得話港台31,32台都有睇，做得好，最like咩節目同點解<br />\n唔好太黃絲feel 同唔好用standard form<br />\n會只當一份意見</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多謝瀏覽我們的網址。如有任何有關廣播事務的查詢，可按以下方式與我們聯絡： <br />\n<br />\n以電子郵件方式傳送至<br />\nba@tela.gov.hk<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3faRZNL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3faRZNL.jpg&h=796e8d00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>以書面方式寄</strong><br />\n廣播事務管理局秘書處<br />\n經影視及娛樂事務管理處<br />\n香港灣仔告士打道5號<br />\n稅務大樓39樓<br />\n(傳真號碼：(852) 2507 2219)<br />\n<br />\n致電查詢電話號碼：(852) 2594 5721"}]}